messages.message: Hi team, it seems that data in the workspace members UI is missing even though it's still there. See screenshots. Link (https://aihub.instabase.com/settings/organizations/ib-internal/workspaces/SolEng_workspace)
`badri-test-service` user is not an org member. I think this user was probably created in correctly and added to the repo via some other ways.
This is expected. Anyone with site admin access should be able to remove this user.
